<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 15:14:20 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>世贸组织称关税往往对穷人造成更严重的打击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/tariffs-tend-hit-poor-harder-wto-says-2024-09-09/</link><description>世界贸易组织周一在一份报告中表示，进口关税往往会对低收入家庭造成不成比例的打击，以反击其认为的对开放市场的抵制和不断上升的保护主义。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 14:32:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/tariffs-tend-hit-poor-harder-wto-says-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>美国提议要求先进人工智能、云提供商报告</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-proposes-requiring-reporting-advanced-ai-cloud-providers-2024-09-09/</link><description>美国商务部周一表示，提议要求先进人工智能开发商和云计算提供商提供详细的报告要求，以确保技术安全并能够抵御网络攻击。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 12:49:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-proposes-requiring-reporting-advanced-ai-cloud-providers-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾参议院第二次认定前市长郭爱丽藐视法庭</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-senate-holds-ex-mayor-alice-guo-contempt-second-time-2024-09-09/</link><description>菲律宾前城镇市长郭爱丽周一第二次受到藐视法庭罪，此前她拒绝回答参议员提出的有关涉嫌与中国犯罪集团有联系以及两个月前她如何逃离菲律宾的问题。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 11:55:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-senate-holds-ex-mayor-alice-guo-contempt-second-time-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>混合动力汽车为铂金属提供了生命线</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/hybrid-cars-throw-lifeline-platinum-metals-2024-09-09/</link><description>随着电动汽车普及率放缓，混合动力汽车销量激增，预计未来几年对铂族金属 (PGM) 的需求将出现意外增长，类似于现在预测的煤炭寿命延长。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 11:55:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/hybrid-cars-throw-lifeline-platinum-metals-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>在苹果 iPhone 16 发布之前，华为三折手机预订量已达 300 万部</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/huawei-racks-up-3-mln-pre-orders-tri-fold-phone-before-apples-iphone-16-reveal-2024-09-09/</link><description>中国科技巨头华为的网站周一显示，其三折叠智能手机的预订量已超过 300 万部，而就在苹果推出新一代 iPhone 的几个小时前。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 11:52:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/huawei-racks-up-3-mln-pre-orders-tri-fold-phone-before-apples-iphone-16-reveal-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平寻求与挪威在绿色能源领域开展“友好”合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-seeks-friendly-cooperation-with-norway-green-energy-evs-2024-09-09/</link><description>国家主席习近平周一在北京对来访的挪威首相斯托雷表示，中国愿与挪威共同推动包括绿色能源在内的“友好”合作。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 11:21:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinas-xi-seeks-friendly-cooperation-with-norway-green-energy-evs-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>德国将军称朝鲜武器增加了俄罗斯库存</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/north-korean-weapons-extending-russian-stockpiles-german-general-says-2024-09-09/</link><description>德国最高军事官员周一在访问韩国时表示，朝鲜提供武器增强了俄罗斯在乌克兰的影响力，使俄罗斯能够将其武器库储存在国内。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 11:20:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/north-korean-weapons-extending-russian-stockpiles-german-general-says-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>拉丁美洲电商之王表示MercadoLibre有巨大的增长空间</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/latin-americas-e-commerce-king-says-mercadolibre-has-huge-room-growth-2024-09-09/</link><description>拉丁美洲电子商务巨头 MercadoLibre Inc（已经是该地区最有价值的上市公司）的首席执行官马科斯·加尔佩林 (Marcos Galperin) 表示，该公司才刚刚起步。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 11:03:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/latin-americas-e-commerce-king-says-mercadolibre-has-huge-room-growth-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：工资发放后的立足点、新 iPhone 和辩论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-09-09/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 10:07:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>独家：黎智英的香港媒体公司高管对 BDO 提起法律诉讼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/execs-jimmy-lais-hong-kong-media-firm-mount-legal-challenge-against-bdo-2024-09-09/</link><description>两名在香港拥有长期经验的西方媒体高管指责国际会计师事务所BDO违反国际规则，帮助香港政府清算该公司，该公司由被监禁的大亨黎智英经营。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 09:46:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/execs-jimmy-lais-hong-kong-media-firm-mount-legal-challenge-against-bdo-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>随着市场升温对冲基金涌向日本</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hedge-funds-flock-japan-market-heats-up-2024-09-09/</link><description>日本在亚洲 4000 亿美元的对冲基金行业中脱颖而出，吸引了基金的推出，而其他地区却遭遇倒闭，这表明 8 月份的剧烈波动并未阻碍日本资本市场的复苏。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 08:25:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/hedge-funds-flock-japan-market-heats-up-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国汽车销量连续第五个月下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-car-sales-fall-fifth-consecutive-month-2024-09-09/</link><description>周一的行业数据显示，中国 8 月份乘用车销量连续第五个月下降，尽管全电动和插电式混合动力车型的销量有所增长，这得益于对驾驶污染较严重的车辆的补贴。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 08:14:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-car-sales-fall-fifth-consecutive-month-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>网易发布即将到来的假期儿童游戏限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/netease-releases-gaming-limits-children-upcoming-holidays-2024-09-09/</link><description>网易游戏周一公布了在即将到来的中秋节和国庆假期期间中国儿童将被允许玩其视频游戏的具体日期和时段。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 08:13:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/netease-releases-gaming-limits-children-upcoming-holidays-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲开发银行称行长浅川将于 2025 年初离职</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-back-ex-fx-tsar-kanda-asian-development-bank-chief-yomiuri-reports-2024-09-09/</link><description>亚洲开发银行周一表示，行长浅川正嗣已宣布打算辞去职务，任期自 2025 年 2 月 23 日起生效。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 07:47:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-back-ex-fx-tsar-kanda-asian-development-bank-chief-yomiuri-reports-2024-09-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国官方媒体称俄罗斯军队将于九月参加中国演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russian-military-join-chinese-exercise-september-says-chinese-state-media-2024-09-09/</link><description>据官方新华社周一报道，俄罗斯军方将派遣海军和空军参加中国九月在日本海和鄂霍次克海举行的演习。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 07:36:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russian-military-join-chinese-exercise-september-says-chinese-state-media-2024-09-09/</guid></item></channel></rss>